    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Armors designed for the Gestech, a form of joust fought with rebated lances, in which one opponent tries to unhorse the other.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
